# Optional local development override for the source imported into root/gsv
# by sys.setup/sys.bootstrap. Wrangler loads the real values from .dev.vars.
#
# GSV_BOOTSTRAP_UPSTREAM accepts either a GitHub owner/repo slug or a git remote URL.
# You can include the ref inline:
# GSV_BOOTSTRAP_UPSTREAM=deathbyknowledge/gsv#my-dev-branch
#
# Or keep source and ref separate:
# GSV_BOOTSTRAP_UPSTREAM=deathbyknowledge/gsv
# GSV_BOOTSTRAP_REF=my-dev-branch
